00:00:02.891 --> 00:00:09.194
Namaste, I'm Lata Jain,
Welcome to Lata's Kitchen

00:00:09.194 --> 00:00:17.055
Sweet saffron rice is a
very delicious dessert

00:00:17.055 --> 00:00:26.977
Today I'm going to make Sweet Saffron Rice, Let's
see the ingredients required for making this

00:00:28.461 --> 00:00:34.588
Long Grained Rice - 1 cup, 
washed and soaked in water for 1 hour

00:00:34.588 --> 00:00:41.955
Sugar - 3/4 cup
( You can also use Powdered Sugar or Bura )

00:00:42.078 --> 00:00:43.523
Water - 2 cups

00:00:43.523 --> 00:00:48.490
Saffron - about 30 threads, 
soaked in milk for 1 hour

00:00:48.503 --> 00:00:50.945
Clarified Butter - 3 tbsp

00:00:50.945 --> 00:00:53.931
Cardamom Powder - 1/2 tsp

00:00:53.931 --> 00:00:56.040
Raisins - 25, washed with water

00:00:56.391 --> 00:00:58.703
Almonds - 1, cut lengthwise

00:00:58.703 --> 00:01:02.455
Cashew nuts - 15, broken into two halves

00:01:02.455 --> 00:01:06.097
Lets start making Sweet Saffron Rice

00:01:06.097 --> 00:01:18.426
Heat clarified butter in a cooker

00:01:21.914 --> 00:01:25.496
Clarified butter is heated,
add cashew nuts to it

00:01:30.945 --> 00:01:44.303
Fry until cashew nuts get
light pink, then add water

00:01:48.344 --> 00:01:51.102
Lets the water boil

00:01:52.047 --> 00:01:56.486
It has boiled, now add the rice

00:02:02.852 --> 00:02:06.793
Mix

00:02:09.914 --> 00:02:17.727
Cover the lid, remove the vent weight
Turn gas to high

00:02:17.727 --> 00:02:22.039
Once pressure is built in the cooker and
steam rushes out, turn flame to low

00:02:22.578 --> 00:02:30.078
Now turn gas to low and
cook it for 15 minutes

00:02:31.133 --> 00:02:37.185
Its been 15 minutes, now turn
off the gas and open the lid

00:02:38.469 --> 00:02:43.258
Add saffron milk

00:02:43.258 --> 00:02:45.846
Add cardamom powder

00:02:46.773 --> 00:02:52.935
Add resins and chopped almonds

00:02:54.703 --> 00:02:58.701
Mix all the ingredients light handedly

00:03:01.906 --> 00:03:09.839
Now ad the sugar and mix light handedly

00:03:13.781 --> 00:03:23.644
Cover the lid and cook for
another 10 minutes on low heat

00:03:24.953 --> 00:03:31.423
Its been 10 minutes, turn off the
gas and let it rest for 10 minutes

00:03:31.423 --> 00:03:38.123
Its been 10 minutes,
Open the lid

00:03:42.195 --> 00:03:48.201
Sweet saffron rice is ready,
now take it out into a plate

00:03:56.969 --> 00:04:00.408
Sweet saffron rice is ready

00:04:00.408 --> 00:04:02.711
It is smelling very good

00:04:02.711 --> 00:04:08.384
You can serve it as sweet
dish with lunch or dinner

00:04:08.384 --> 00:04:11.717
Thanks for watching Sweet Saffron Rice

